Argentina won the 2022 FIFA World Cup in Qatar, but a fan token connected to the team is collapsing.<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
The Argentine Football Association Fan Token, offered through partnerships with Socios, jumped to $6.40 on Dec. 18, the day of the FIFA World Cup Final, before falling 58% to $2.67 on Dec. 20.&nbsp;
